  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find and collect over 1000 gems on your journey toward Calculus Castle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374590/extras/3dc7e03a008a8f7fd127ed90b64f2736.poster.avif?t=1743794764\" width=800 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374590/extras/3dc7e03a008a8f7fd127ed90b64f2736.webm?t=1743794764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374590/extras/3dc7e03a008a8f7fd127ed90b64f2736.mp4?t=1743794764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore 8 unique levels on your quest</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special unlocks and secret levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete for the fastest level completion time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn achievements that unlock new skins for Lewis</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourself with Hard Mode - with super tough precision platforming</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try and collect every gem in each level!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374590/extras/c30161fd1b5c5bb0efc63f6292b5deda.poster.avif?t=1743794764\" width=800 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374590/extras/c30161fd1b5c5bb0efc63f6292b5deda.webm?t=1743794764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374590/extras/c30161fd1b5c5bb0efc63f6292b5deda.mp4?t=1743794764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find and collect over 1000 gems on your journey toward Calculus Castle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374590/extras/3dc7e03a008a8f7fd127ed90b64f2736.poster.avif?t=1743794764\" width=800 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374590/extras/3dc7e03a008a8f7fd127ed90b64f2736.webm?t=1743794764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374590/extras/3dc7e03a008a8f7fd127ed90b64f2736.mp4?t=1743794764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore 8 unique levels on your quest</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special unlocks and secret levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete for the fastest level completion time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn achievements that unlock new skins for Lewis</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourself with Hard Mode - with super tough precision platforming</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try and collect every gem in each level!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374590/extras/c30161fd1b5c5bb0efc63f6292b5deda.poster.avif?t=1743794764\" width=800 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374590/extras/c30161fd1b5c5bb0efc63f6292b5deda.webm?t=1743794764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3374590/extras/c30161fd1b5c5bb0efc63f6292b5deda.mp4?t=1743794764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
